        {
            "title": "Anthropic推出Claude Opus 4.7 強化編碼能力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lLdBaG87BBpyRsw_qunzPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/STOCK-EXCHANGE-RUSSIAN-TRADING-SYSTEMS_M_1440048891.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>週四發布了Claude Opus 4.7,標誌著其先前Opus 4.6模型的升級,在軟件工程和視覺能力方面均有所改進。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Anthropic的說法,新模型在處理以往需要密切監督的複雜編碼任務方面取得了進展。Opus 4.7可處理長邊解析度高達2,576像素的圖像,是先前Claude模型容量的三倍以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管Opus 4.7代表了一項進步,但它的能力仍不及Claude Mythos Preview——Anthropic最強大的模型。由於上週公佈的Glasswing項目中概述的安全問題,Mythos Preview繼續限量發布。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f9e1dbd1-7e12-35fa-b2a4-15f4de8fdc88-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic在Opus 4.7中實施了網絡安全防護措施,可自動檢測並阻止表明禁止或高風險網絡安全用途的請求。與Mythos Preview相比,該公司在訓練期間降低了該模型的網絡能力。安全專業人員可以通過Anthropic新推出的網絡驗證計劃,將該模型用於合法的網絡安全工作。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該模型可在Claude產品、Claude API、Amazon Bedrock、Google Cloud的Vertex AI和Microsoft Foundry上使用。定價與Opus 4.6保持不變,為每百萬輸入代幣5美元,每百萬輸出代幣25美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Opus 4.7在包括金融代理評估和GDPval-AA在內的基準測試中得分高於其前身,後者衡量金融和法律領域具有經濟價值的知識工作。該模型顯示出改進的指令遵循能力,儘管Anthropic指出這可能需要用戶調整為早期模型編寫的提示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic在高級和最大設置之間引入了新的「xhigh」努力級別,為推理能力和響應速度之間的平衡提供了額外的控制。該公司還為API用戶推出了處於公開測試階段的任務預算,並在Claude Code中添加了用於錯誤檢測的ultrareview命令。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更新後的模型使用新的代幣化器,根據內容類型,相同輸入可能產生1.0至1.35倍的代幣數量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/anthropic%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAclaude-opus-4-7-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E7%B7%A8%E7%A2%BC%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B-153608639.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 00:28:06",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
